======================================================================
Scripts to Run Software From Startup
======================================================================

- copy the service file to /lib/systemd/system/
- copy the bash script to /usr/startscripts/
- edit the "binary" variable in the script to either run the "robot" or "basestation" software.
- $ systemctl daemon-reload
- $ systemctl enable start_bushbot.service
- copy the project binary files to /Bushbot/